name: Design your own
description:
Design your own Baby grow, Sleep suit or T-Shirts, for that special occasion or just a bit of fun. Ideal for parties, special events, birthdays or a great gift to a loved one.

Please tell us the colour of garment you would like along with quote, text or name you require using PayPal note to seller option at checkout.

We will then send you a proof copy of your design for your approval before your garment is produced.

Please don't hesitate to contact us with your requirements, we are always happy to help.
